        "subject": "Congratulations! You Have Been Selected for the Technical Youth Trainer Position",
        "message": "=<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <title>Congratulations! You Have Been Selected</title>\n</head>\n<body style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333333;\">\n\n    <p>Dear <strong>{{$node[\"Parse JSON\"].json.name}}</strong>,</p>\n\n    <p>Greetings!</p>\n\n    <p>\n        Thank you for submitting your resume for the <strong>AI Developer</strong> position.\n    </p>\n\n    <p>\n        We are pleased to inform you that, based on our resume screening process, your profile has been selected for the next stage of the recruitment process.\n    </p>\n\n    <p>\n        Your skills, qualifications, and experience closely match our requirements, and we are excited to move forward with your application.\n    </p>\n\n    <p>\n        Our HR team will contact you shortly with further details regarding the interview schedule and the next steps.\n    </p>\n\n    <p>\n        Please reply to this email to confirm that you have received this notification.\n    </p>\n\n    <p>\n        We look forward to having you as part of our organization.\n    </p>\n\n    <p>\n        Best Regards,<br>\n        HR Team<br>\n        ABC Technologies Pvt. Ltd.\n    </p>\n\n</body>\n</html>",
